{"id": "1422232523034984539", "channel_id": "1422232523034984539", "type": 0, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hey all,\n\nThe past few DTides (regional zone effects), the jump in health and difficulty from Alert 3 to Alert 4 is really high.\n\nThe game is kinda getting boring. \n\nThere are a few of us players that think we don't even need to think on Alert 3 and can easily clear it. \n\nBut then Alert 4 jump in health (especially for bosses) is so big that we can't clear it.\n\nSo we are in this zone where A3 is way too easy and A4 is way too hard. \n\nPlease fix this! Because we are losing fun for playing the game being in this, boring zone.", "timestamp": "2025-09-29T14:44:17.294000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1422232523034984539", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Alert 4 difficulty", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
